graphics.name: Tropane, piperidine and pyridine alkaloid biosynthesis

nodes.name: LysW-gamma-L-lysine amidohydrolase
nodes.rxn: LysW-gamma-L-lysine + H2O <=> L-Lysine + alpha-Aminoadipate carrier protein LysW

nodes.name: LysW-gamma-L-alpha-aminoadipate 6-semialdehyde:NADP+ 6-oxidoreductase (phosphorylating)
nodes.rxn: LysW-gamma-L-alpha-aminoadipyl 6-phosphate + NADPH + H+ <=> LysW-gamma-L-alpha-aminoadipate 6-semialdehyde + NADP+ + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: LysW:L-2-aminoadipate ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: L-2-Aminoadipate + alpha-Aminoadipate carrier protein LysW + ATP <=> LysW-gamma-L-alpha-aminoadipate + ADP + Orthophosphate

nodes.name: meso-2,6-diaminoheptanedioate:NADP+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: meso-2,6-Diaminoheptanedioate + NADP+ + H2O <=> L-2-Amino-6-oxoheptanedioate + Ammonia + NADPH + H+

nodes.name: N6-(L-1,3-Dicarboxypropyl)-L-lysine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (L-lysine-forming)
nodes.rxn: N6-(L-1,3-Dicarboxypropyl)-L-lysine + NAD+ + H2O <=> L-Lysine + 2-Oxoglutarate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: N6-(L-1,3-Dicarboxypropyl)-L-lysine:NADP+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: N6-(L-1,3-Dicarboxypropyl)-L-lysine + NADP+ + H2O <=> L-Glutamate + L-2-Aminoadipate 6-semialdehyde + NADPH + H+

nodes.name: L-2-aminoadipate-6-semialdehyde:NADP+ 6-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: alpha-Aminoadipoyl-S-acyl enzyme + NADPH + H+ <=> L-2-Aminoadipate 6-semialdehyde + Holo-Lys2 + NADP+

nodes.name: L-2-aminoadipate-6-semialdehyde:NADP+ 6-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: L-2-Aminoadipate adenylate + Holo-Lys2 <=> alpha-Aminoadipoyl-S-acyl enzyme + AMP

nodes.name: L-Lysine + (2R,3R)-3-Methylornithine + ATP <=> (2R,3R)-3-Methylornithinyl-N6-lysine + Products of ATP breakdown
nodes.rxn: L-Lysine + (2R,3R)-3-Methylornithine + ATP <=> (2R,3R)-3-Methylornithinyl-N6-lysine + Products of ATP breakdown
